cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.MA, cs.DS, cs.PL 

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on developing a logic-based framework for formal specification and algorithmic verification. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper deals with multi-agent systems and their properties. 
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is another possible category as the paper specifically deals with homogeneous and dynamic concurrent multi-agent transition systems. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper develops an algorithm for global model checking of formulae in normal form. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with formal specification and verification of systems.
